comments.body:
@mheon , to implement this, I think we would need to extend the OCI specification to support "Resources" in the `process` section: https://github.com/opencontainers/runtime-spec/blob/main/schema/config-schema.json#L62-L238.

Without that, we would have to do all the heave-lifting in the Podman which is not something we should do afaik.

I can start a discussion there asking for an opinions on that, if that's aligned with your expectations about this ticket.
